<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>O.M.STOR</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    body{
      background:#fff;
      color:#111;
    }

    a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:inherit;
    }

    header{
      width:100%;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      padding:22px 60px;
      background:#fff;
      border-bottom:1px solid #eee;
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:1000;
    }

    .logo{
      font-size:28px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:2px;
    }

    .logo span{
      color:#ff5a1f;
    }

    nav{
      display:flex;
      gap:30px;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:14px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    nav a:hover{
      color:#ff5a1f;
    }

    .hero{
      min-height:90vh;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      align-items:center;
      padding:60px;
      background:linear-gradient(to right, #f5f5f5 50%, #ffffff 50%);
    }

    .hero-text h1{
      font-size:64px;
      line-height:1.05;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:20px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .hero-text p{
      font-size:18px;
      color:#666;
      margin-bottom:30px;
      max-width:500px;
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .hero-buttons{
      display:flex;
      gap:15px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .btn{
      padding:14px 28px;
      border-radius:30px;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:14px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      transition:.3s;
      display:inline-block;
    }

    .btn-dark{
      background:#111;
      color:#fff;
    }

    .btn-dark:hover{
      background:#ff5a1f;
    }

    .btn-light{
      border:2px solid #111;
      color:#111;
      background:#fff;
    }

    .btn-light:hover{
      border-color:#ff5a1f;
      color:#ff5a1f;
    }

    .hero-image{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .hero-image img{
      width:100%;
      max-width:600px;
      border-radius:25px;
      box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      object-fit:cover;
    }

    .section{
      padding:80px 60px;
    }

    .section-title{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:end;
      margin-bottom:40px;
      gap:20px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .section-title h2{
      font-size:38px;
      font-weight:800;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .section-title p{
      color:#777;
      max-width:500px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .products{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap:25px;
    }

    .card{
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:20px;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      transition:.3s;
      border:1px solid #eee;
    }

    .card:hover{
      transform:translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .card img{
      width:100%;
      height:280px;
      object-fit:cover;
      display:block;
    }

    .card-content{
      padding:20px;
    }

    .category{
      color:#ff5a1f;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .card-content h3{
      font-size:22px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .card-content p{
      color:#777;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.6;
      margin-bottom:15px;
    }

    .price-row{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .price{
      font-weight:800;
      font-size:20px;
    }

    .buy-btn{
      background:#111;
      color:#fff;
      padding:10px 18px;
      border-radius:25px;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .buy-btn:hover{
      background:#ff5a1f;
    }

    .banner{
      margin:40px 60px;
      background:#111;
      color:#fff;
      border-radius:30px;
      padding:70px 50px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .banner h2{
      font-size:42px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .banner p{
      color:#ddd;
      max-width:700px;
      margin:0 auto 25px;
      line-height:1.8;
    }

    .features{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap:20px;
    }

    .feature{
      background:#f8f8f8;
      padding:30px;
      border-radius:20px;
    }

    .feature h3{
      margin-bottom:10px;
      font-size:20px;
    }

    .feature p{
      color:#666;
      line-height:1.6;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    footer{
      margin-top:60px;
      background:#111;
      color:#fff;
      padding:50px 60px 30px;
    }

    .footer-top{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap:30px;
      margin-bottom:30px;
    }

    .footer-brand h2{
      font-size:28px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
    }

    .footer-brand p,
    .footer-links a{
      color:#bbb;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.8;
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .footer-links h4{
      margin-bottom:15px;
      font-size:16px;
      color:#fff;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .copyright{
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding-top:20px;
      color:#999;
      font-size:13px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    @media(max-width: 900px){
      .hero{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
        padding:40px 20px;
        gap:30px;
      }

      .hero-text h1{
        font-size:42px;
      }

      header{
        padding:18px 20px;
        flex-direction:column;
        gap:15px;
      }

      nav{
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        justify-content:center;
        gap:15px;
      }

      .section{
        padding:60px 20px;
      }

      .banner{
        margin:20px;
        padding:50px 25px;
      }

      .banner h2{
        font-size:30px;
      }

      .footer-top{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .card img{
        height:220px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">O.<span>M</span>.STOR</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">New</a>
      <a href="#">Men</a>
      <a href="#">Women</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Move with style.</h1>
      <p>
        Discover premium fashion and sportswear inspired by modern street style.
        O.M.STOR brings you bold products, clean design, and a professional shopping experience.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-dark">Shop Now</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-light">Explore More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Product">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Featured Products</h2>
      <p>Clean, powerful, and modern products selected for customers who love premium quality and urban style.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="products">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549298916-b41d501d3772?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Product 1">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="category">Sneakers</div>
          <h3>O.M Air Black</h3>
          <p>Premium sneakers with lightweight comfort and modern details.</p>
          <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price">\$89</div>
            <a href="#" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523398002811-999ca8dec234?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Product 2">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="category">Hoodie</div>
          <h3>Urban Fit Hoodie</h3>
          <p>Soft fabric, oversized cut, and clean everyday streetwear look.</p>
          <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price">\$59</div>
            <a href="#" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515886657613-9f3515b0c78f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Product 3">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="category">Women</div>
          <h3>Street Motion Set</h3>
          <p>Designed for confidence, movement, and minimalist fashion lovers.</p>
          <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price">\$74</div>
            <a href="#" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503342217505-b0a15ec3261c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Product 4">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="category">Accessories</div>
          <h3>O.M Cap Pro</h3>
          <p>A clean finishing touch for your everyday premium outfit.</p>
          <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price">\$29</div>
            <a href="#" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="banner">
    <h2>New Collection 2025</h2>
    <p>
      Powerful looks, premium materials, and a bold identity made for people
      who want more than just clothing. Welcome to the next level of style with O.M.STOR.
    </p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-dark">Discover Collection</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
      <p>We focus on performance, quality, and clean presentation to make your shopping experience simple and premium.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Premium Quality</h3>
        <p>High-end materials and careful finishing for a professional brand image.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
        <p>Quick shipping options to keep your experience smooth and reliable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Modern Design</h3>
        <p>Inspired by leading sportswear and streetwear store experiences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Trusted Support</h3>
        <p>Professional customer care for orders, sizing, and product information.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h2>O.M.STOR</h2>
        <p>Modern store for fashion, sneakers, and premium streetwear with a clean professional identity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>Shop</h4>
        <a href="#">Sneakers</a>
        <a href="#">Clothing</a>
        <a href="#">Accessories</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>Support</h4>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
        <a href="#">Delivery</a>
        <a href="#">Returns</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>Follow</h4>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#">TikTok</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="copyright">
      © 2025 O.M.STOR — All Rights Reserved
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
